        <mxCell id="WuGufPFb8vr9SFG-igHj-9" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul style=&quot;margin: 16px 0px; padding-left: 18px; color: rgb(15, 17, 21); font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &amp;quot;Open Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;ds-markdown-paragraph&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0px !important; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 600;&quot;&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: 100%; line-height: 22px; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-language-override: normal; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;quot;Cascadia Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Ubuntu Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Liberation Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;JetBrains Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Fira Code&amp;quot;, Cousine, &amp;quot;Roboto Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, Courier, sans-serif, system-ui; background-color: rgb(235, 238, 242); border-radius: 6px; align-items: center; padding: 0px 5px; display: inline-flex; font-size: 0.875em !important;&quot;&gt;cc_library&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/span&gt;：定义一个 C++ 库，可以被其他代码链接使用。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin-top: 6px;&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;ds-markdown-paragraph&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0px !important; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 600;&quot;&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: 100%; line-height: 22px; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-language-override: normal; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;quot;Cascadia Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Ubuntu Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Liberation Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;JetBrains Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Fira Code&amp;quot;, Cousine, &amp;quot;Roboto Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, Courier, sans-serif, system-ui; background-color: rgb(235, 238, 242); border-radius: 6px; align-items: center; padding: 0px 5px; display: inline-flex; font-size: 0.875em !important;&quot;&gt;cc_test&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/span&gt;：定义一个测试程序，用来验证库的正确性。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin-top: 6px;&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;ds-markdown-paragraph&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0px !important; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 600;&quot;&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: 100%; line-height: 22px; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-language-override: normal; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;quot;Cascadia Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Ubuntu Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Liberation Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;JetBrains Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Fira Code&amp;quot;, Cousine, &amp;quot;Roboto Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, Courier, sans-serif, system-ui; background-color: rgb(235, 238, 242); border-radius: 6px; align-items: center; padding: 0px 5px; display: inline-flex; font-size: 0.875em !important;&quot;&gt;name&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/span&gt;：这个目标的名字，其他目标可以通过&amp;nbsp;&lt;code style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: 100%; line-height: 22px; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-language-override: normal; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;quot;Cascadia Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Ubuntu Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Liberation Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;JetBrains Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Fira Code&amp;quot;, Cousine, &amp;quot;Roboto Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, Courier, sans-serif, system-ui; background-color: rgb(235, 238, 242); border-radius: 6px; align-items: center; padding: 0px 5px; display: inline-flex; font-size: 0.875em !important;&quot;&gt;//路径:名字&lt;/code&gt;&amp;nbsp;来依赖它。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin-top: 6px;&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;ds-markdown-paragraph&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0px !important; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 600;&quot;&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: 100%; line-height: 22px; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-language-override: normal; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;quot;Cascadia Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Ubuntu Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Liberation Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;JetBrains Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Fira Code&amp;quot;, Cousine, &amp;quot;Roboto Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, Courier, sans-serif, system-ui; background-color: rgb(235, 238, 242); border-radius: 6px; align-items: center; padding: 0px 5px; display: inline-flex; font-size: 0.875em !important;&quot;&gt;hdrs&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/span&gt;：对外公开的头文件（.h）。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin-top: 6px;&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;ds-markdown-paragraph&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0px !important; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 600;&quot;&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: 100%; line-height: 22px; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-language-override: normal; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;quot;Cascadia Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Ubuntu Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Liberation Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;JetBrains Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Fira Code&amp;quot;, Cousine, &amp;quot;Roboto Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, Courier, sans-serif, system-ui; background-color: rgb(235, 238, 242); border-radius: 6px; align-items: center; padding: 0px 5px; display: inline-flex; font-size: 0.875em !important;&quot;&gt;srcs&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/span&gt;：实现文件（.cc）。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin-top: 6px;&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;ds-markdown-paragraph&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0px !important; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 600;&quot;&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: 100%; line-height: 22px; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-language-override: normal; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;quot;Cascadia Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Ubuntu Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Liberation Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;JetBrains Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Fira Code&amp;quot;, Cousine, &amp;quot;Roboto Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, Courier, sans-serif, system-ui; background-color: rgb(235, 238, 242); border-radius: 6px; align-items: center; padding: 0px 5px; display: inline-flex; font-size: 0.875em !important;&quot;&gt;deps&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/span&gt;：依赖的其他库（本目录或其他目录的）。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin-top: 6px;&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;ds-markdown-paragraph&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0px !important; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 600;&quot;&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: 100%; line-height: 22px; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-language-override: normal; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;quot;Cascadia Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Ubuntu Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Liberation Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;JetBrains Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Fira Code&amp;quot;, Cousine, &amp;quot;Roboto Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, Courier, sans-serif, system-ui; background-color: rgb(235, 238, 242); border-radius: 6px; align-items: center; padding: 0px 5px; display: inline-flex; font-size: 0.875em !important;&quot;&gt;visibility&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/span&gt;：控制哪些其他目录可以依赖这个库（&lt;code style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: 100%; line-height: 22px; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-language-override: normal; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;quot;Cascadia Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Ubuntu Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Liberation Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;JetBrains Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Fira Code&amp;quot;, Cousine, &amp;quot;Roboto Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, Courier, sans-serif, system-ui; background-color: rgb(235, 238, 242); border-radius: 6px; align-items: center; padding: 0px 5px; display: inline-flex; font-size: 0.875em !important;&quot;&gt;PUBLIC&lt;/code&gt;&amp;nbsp;表示所有人都能用；&lt;code style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: 100%; line-height: 22px; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-language-override: normal; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;quot;Cascadia Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Ubuntu Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Liberation Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;JetBrains Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Fira Code&amp;quot;, Cousine, &amp;quot;Roboto Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, Courier, sans-serif, system-ui; background-color: rgb(235, 238, 242); border-radius: 6px; align-items: center; padding: 0px 5px; display: inline-flex; font-size: 0.875em !important;&quot;&gt;//flare/...&lt;/code&gt;&amp;nbsp;表示只有&amp;nbsp;&lt;code style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: 100%; line-height: 22px; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-language-override: normal; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;quot;Cascadia Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Ubuntu Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Liberation Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;JetBrains Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Fira Code&amp;quot;, Cousine, &amp;quot;Roboto Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, Courier, sans-serif, system-ui; background-color: rgb(235, 238, 242); border-radius: 6px; align-items: center; padding: 0px 5px; display: inline-flex; font-size: 0.875em !important;&quot;&gt;flare&lt;/code&gt;&amp;nbsp;目录下的代码能用）&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;" vertex="1">
